object.customQuery:
SELECT DISTINCT 
q.cmm_container AS underwriting_question_and_answer_type,
q.id AS underwriting_question_and_answer_row_source_system_key,
q.system_id AS source_system_system_id, 
q.id AS source_system_id,q.parent_id AS source_system_parent_id,
q.name AS underwriting_question_code,
q.value AS underwriting_answer,
q.visible_ind AS question_visible_on_acx_ui_indicator ,
q.text AS text,
q.display_desc AS display_description,
q.row_id AS source_system_row_id,
qrpcr.parent_child_indicator AS parent_or_child_indicator,
qrpcr.question AS parent_question_of_child_question,
qrpcr.priority_order AS question_and_answer_hierarchy,
qrpcr.display_when_reply_is_no_or_null as display_when_reply_is_no_or_null,
qrpcr.display_when_reply_is_yes_or_not_null as display_when_reply_is_yes_or_not_null
FROM bronze.acx_question_reply q
LEFT JOIN dbo.policy_risk_key_reference prkr
ON q.system_id = prkr.policy_system_id
AND q.cmm_container = prkr.policy_cmm_container 
LEFT JOIN bronze.question_reply_parent_child_reference_for_homeowners qrpcr
ON q.name = qrpcr.question
WHERE prkr.line_of_business = 'Homeowners'
AND prkr.policy_risk_key_reference_row_effective_end_date = '9999-12-31'
AND qrpcr.question_reply_parent_child_reference_ho_row_effective_end_datetime  = '9999-12-31';

fields.name: o_question_visible_on_acx_ui_indicator
fields.expression:
decode(true,
question_visible_on_acx_ui_indicator = 'Y','YES',
question_visible_on_acx_ui_indicator = 'Yes','YES',
question_visible_on_acx_ui_indicator = 'N','NO',
question_visible_on_acx_ui_indicator = 'No','NO',
question_visible_on_acx_ui_indicator = '',NULL,
NULL)

fields.name: v_parent_display_indicator
fields.expression: IIF(parent_or_child_indicator='C' AND (ISNULL(underwriting_answer) OR underwriting_answer = 'No'), display_when_reply_is_no_or_null, display_when_reply_is_yes_or_not_null)

object.customQuery:
select 
	underwriting_question_and_answer_id as underwriting_question_and_answer_id,
	underwriting_question_and_answer_row_md5checksum,
	underwriting_question_and_answer_row_effective_end_datetime,
	underwriting_question_and_answer_row_source_system_key,
	source_system_system_id,
	underwriting_question_and_answer_type,
	underwriting_question_code
from
	silver.underwriting_questions_and_answers
where
	underwriting_question_and_answer_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
order by source_system_system_id, underwriting_question_and_answer_type ;

attributes.name: Download S3 Files In Multiple Parts

fields.name: src_md5_hash_value
fields.expression:
MD5(
'underwriting_question_and_answer_type' || underwriting_question_and_answer_type ||
'underwriting_question_and_answer_row_source_system_key' || underwriting_question_and_answer_row_source_system_key ||
'source_system_system_id' || to_char(source_system_system_id) ||
'source_system_id' || to_char(source_system_id) ||
'source_system_parent_id' || source_system_parent_id ||
'underwriting_question_code' || underwriting_question_code ||
'underwriting_answer' || underwriting_answer ||
'question_visible_on_acx_ui_indicator' || question_visible_on_acx_ui_indicator ||
'text' || text ||
'display_description' || display_description ||
'source_system_row_id' || to_char(source_system_row_id) ||
'parent_or_child_indicator' || parent_or_child_indicator ||
'parent_question_of_child_question' || parent_question_of_child_question ||
'question_and_answer_hierarchy' || to_char(question_and_answer_hierarchy) ||
'display_when_reply_is_no_or_null' || display_when_reply_is_no_or_null ||
'display_when_reply_is_yes_or_not_null' || display_when_reply_is_yes_or_not_null
)
